  schema:name "Allium × proliferum" ;
  schema:description "Sterile perennial hybrid between Allium cepa and Allium fistulosum, reproduces exclusively via aerial topset bulbils, hardy zones 3-10 with distinctive \"walking\" dispersal behavior." ;
